track_notes:
classification EE expert  very hard for strong SOTA-lovers.  about 1600 mt and 5 Hours rise
With my friend Fabrizio IZ1DNQ . 
Road closed at S.Bartolomeo. Signed path only in the first half part. Climbing on the rocks in the higher part. Would be better have helmets for safety in case of tumble. 
more details on www.sotaitalia.it/files/ciorneva.pdf
track_title: class EE Hard and long Trek Rocky summit NO path No phone
